{
  "stem": "22734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, when these 1,500 men really left and we saw them boarding the train because we were so-- you know-- when they marched and when they boarded the train and they left, everything was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] maybe I should-- digress.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You wanted to hear when we were tattooed, because that's part of my story, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were tattooed about a week later, after we arrived to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were tattooed by Polish girls who came from the women's camp and tattooed us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was-- and the girl-- the girl who tattooed me and my friend, her name was Helena.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, if you-- and we started to talk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she said she has been in that camp forever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was human.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said, if you ever need anything, I am in the woman's camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and look me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'll help you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then we-- and that was that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So after the-- so I am coming back to-- to our story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After the men left, at about three, four days later, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the mothers of the children were called together by-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know whether it was an SS man, or by somebody from the registry.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they were told that these children are doomed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the mother had a choice to go with them, or to go through the selection, which will take place on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was, I don't know, Thursday, Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's up to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It-- if they go through the selection, there is a chance that they will make it and they'll go-- and they will be working in Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
